---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI Novice — 비주얼로 이해하는 AI 교육 가이드">

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-badge">Visual AI Education · 2026</div>
  <h1>복잡한 AI 개념을<br><em>눈으로 이해하다</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">텍스트 벽이 아닌, 도식·다이어그램·인터랙션으로<br>AI의 원리부터 실전까지 직관적으로 배우는 교육 가이드</p>
</section>

<!-- SITE CONCEPT -->
<section style="max-width:920px;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 1.5rem 2rem;">

  <!-- What makes this different -->
  <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
    <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.75rem;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:.8rem">What Makes This Different</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--display);font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3.5vw,2.2rem);font-weight:800;color:var(--white);line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:1rem">교과서가 아닌, 시각 가이드</h2>
  </div>

  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:1rem;margin-bottom:3rem">
    <div style="background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center">
      <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:.6rem">🎨</div>
      <div style="font-size:.92rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.3rem">비주얼 퍼스트</div>
      <div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.7">모든 개념을 도식·플로우·<br>다이어그램으로 시각화</div>
    </div>
    <div style="background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center">
      <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:.6rem">🧩</div>
      <div style="font-size:.92rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.3rem">비개발자 친화</div>
      <div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.7">코딩 경험 없이도<br>이해 가능한 수준부터</div>
    </div>
    <div style="background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center">
      <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:.6rem">🔄</div>
      <div style="font-size:.92rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.3rem">인터랙티브</div>
      <div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.7">탭·토글·체크리스트로<br>능동적 학습</div>
    </div>
    <div style="background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center">
      <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:.6rem">🌗</div>
      <div style="font-size:.92rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.3rem">다크 / 라이트</div>
      <div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.7">환경에 맞춰<br>편안하게 학습</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Learning Path -->
  <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.75rem;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:.8rem;text-align:center">Learning Path</div>

  <!-- Part Cards -->
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:1.2rem;margin-bottom:3rem">
    <a href="/00-llm" style="background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--violet)';this.style.transform='translateY(-4px)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--border)';this.style.transform='translateY(0)'">
      <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:.8rem">🧠</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.7rem;color:var(--violet);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:.3rem">PART 0 · 기초 다지기</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.6rem">LLM 완전 이해</div>
      <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem">AI의 핵심 엔진, 거대 언어 모델. 트랜스포머부터 토큰, 문장 생성 원리까지 직관적으로.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.3rem">
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--violet-dim);color:var(--violet);border:1px solid rgba(124,108,240,0.3)">트랜스포머</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--violet-dim);color:var(--violet);border:1px solid rgba(124,108,240,0.3)">토큰</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--violet-dim);color:var(--violet);border:1px solid rgba(124,108,240,0.3)">GPT vs BERT</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--violet-dim);color:var(--violet);border:1px solid rgba(124,108,240,0.3)">할루시네이션</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/01-ai-agents" style="background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--teal)';this.style.transform='translateY(-4px)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--border)';this.style.transform='translateY(0)'">
      <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:.8rem">🤖</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.7rem;color:var(--teal);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:.3rem">PART 1 · 이해하기</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.6rem">AI Agents 완전 가이드</div>
      <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem">LLM의 원리부터 Memory, Tools, Planning, Multi-Agent까지 — AI 에이전트의 구조를 도식으로 이해합니다.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.3rem">
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--teal-bg);color:var(--teal);border:1px solid var(--teal-border)">LLM</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--teal-bg);color:var(--teal);border:1px solid var(--teal-border)">Memory</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--teal-bg);color:var(--teal);border:1px solid var(--teal-border)">Tools · MCP</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--teal-bg);color:var(--teal);border:1px solid var(--teal-border)">Planning</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--teal-bg);color:var(--teal);border:1px solid var(--teal-border)">Multi-Agent</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/02-vibe-basic" style="background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--accent)';this.style.transform='translateY(-4px)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--border)';this.style.transform='translateY(0)'">
      <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:.8rem">💻</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.7rem;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:.3rem">PART 2 · 만들어보기</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.6rem">바이브코딩 입문</div>
      <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem">코딩 경험 없이 AI에게 지시해서 실제 서비스를 만드는 방법. 프롬프트부터 배포까지.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.3rem">
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--accent-bg);color:var(--accent);border:1px solid var(--accent-border)">프롬프트</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--accent-bg);color:var(--accent);border:1px solid var(--accent-border)">HTML/CSS/JS</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--accent-bg);color:var(--accent);border:1px solid var(--accent-border)">Git · 배포</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--accent-bg);color:var(--accent);border:1px solid var(--accent-border)">Docker</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/03-vibe-master" style="background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--accent)';this.style.transform='translateY(-4px)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--border)';this.style.transform='translateY(0)'">
      <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:.8rem">🚀</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.7rem;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:.3rem">PART 3 · 깊게 파기</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.6rem">바이브코딩 심화</div>
      <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem">하네스 엔지니어링, TDD/SDD, 멀티 에이전트까지 — 프로덕션 수준의 AI 코딩.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.3rem">
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--accent-bg);color:var(--accent);border:1px solid var(--accent-border)">하네스</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--accent-bg);color:var(--accent);border:1px solid var(--accent-border)">CLAUDE.md</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--accent-bg);color:var(--accent);border:1px solid var(--accent-border)">멀티 에이전트</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/04-power-platform" style="background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--blue)';this.style.transform='translateY(-4px)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--border)';this.style.transform='translateY(0)'">
      <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:.8rem">⚡</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.7rem;color:var(--blue);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:.3rem">PART 4 · 업무 적용</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.6rem">Power Platform</div>
      <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem">코딩 없이 앱·자동화·AI 에이전트를 만드는 Microsoft 노코드 플랫폼.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.3rem">
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--blue-bg);color:var(--blue);border:1px solid var(--blue-border)">Power Apps</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--blue-bg);color:var(--blue);border:1px solid var(--blue-border)">Power Automate</span>
        <span style="font-size:.68rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:var(--blue-bg);color:var(--blue);border:1px solid var(--blue-border)">Copilot Studio</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Learning Flow -->
  <div style="background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:2.5rem 2rem;margin-bottom:2rem">
    <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-dim);letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:1.5rem;text-align:center">Learning Flow</div>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:.8rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:.3rem;min-width:95px">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--violet-dim);border:1px solid rgba(124,108,240,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.4rem">🧠</div>
        <div style="font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--violet)">LLM 기초</div>
      </div>
      <div style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:1.2rem">→</div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:.3rem;min-width:95px">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--teal-bg);border:1px solid var(--teal-border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.4rem">🤖</div>
        <div style="font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--teal)">AI Agent</div>
      </div>
      <div style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:1.2rem">→</div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:.3rem;min-width:95px">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--accent-bg);border:1px solid var(--accent-border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.4rem">💻</div>
        <div style="font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)">만들어보기</div>
      </div>
      <div style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:1.2rem">→</div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:.3rem;min-width:95px">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--accent-bg);border:1px solid var(--accent-border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.4rem">🚀</div>
        <div style="font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)">깊게 파기</div>
      </div>
      <div style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:1.2rem">→</div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:.3rem;min-width:95px">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--blue-bg);border:1px solid var(--blue-border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.4rem">⚡</div>
        <div style="font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue)">업무 적용</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Start Button -->
  <div style="text-align:center;padding:2rem 0;">
    <a href="/00-llm" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;padding:.8rem 2rem;border:1.5px solid var(--violet);background:var(--violet-dim);color:var(--violet);border-radius:12px;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;font-family:var(--sans);text-decoration:none" onmouseover="this.style.background='var(--violet)';this.style.color='#fff'" onmouseout="this.style.background='var(--violet-dim)';this.style.color='var(--violet)'">
      LLM 기초부터 시작하기 <span style="font-size:1.2rem">→</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
